{"id":309155,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/08/奇闻录-盛世一景-8-16/","date":"2013-08-16T22:15:29Z","modified":"2013-08-16T22:15:29Z","title":"奇闻录 | 盛世一景 8-16","content":"<p><p>范振，1918年出生，17岁投笔从戎参加抗日战争，辗转江浙沪一带，参加了淞沪、鄂西、石牌会战等多次大战，无数小战，受伤多次，曾因为作战英勇，范老受到蒋介石的亲自嘉奖。如今经济十分拮据，没有退休工资、无医保，仅有黄埔同学会补助和高龄补贴。1949年他念及老父未走台湾，后被认定为反革命分子劳改30多年。如今范老卧病在床，只求国家和人民认同。<span></span></p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://qiwen.lu/20445.html/eca86bd9da851377aabf23\"><img class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-20446\" alt=\"eca86bd9da851377aabf23\" src=\"https://qiwen.lu/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/eca86bd9da851377aabf23.jpg\" width=\"500\" /></a></p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://qiwen.lu/20445.html/eca86bd9da851377aabf24\"><img class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-20447\" alt=\"eca86bd9da851377aabf24\" src=\"https://qiwen.lu/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/eca86bd9da851377aabf24.jpg\" width=\"500\" /></a></p>\n<p>相关：<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://edu.gmw.cn/2013-08/16/content_8616879.htm\">废弃厂房里的抗战老兵</a></p>\n<div>\n<div>\n<h3>猜你喜欢</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://qiwen.lu/19433.html\">盛世一景 7-22</a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://qiwen.lu/19333.html\">盛世一景 7-20</a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://qiwen.lu/20286.html\">盛世一景 8-12</a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://qiwen.lu/19360.html\">盛世一景 7-21</a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://qiwen.lu/20352.html\">盛世一景 8-14</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder